Title: Fix calculation of soft query limit in HW/SW inventory views
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1616421597
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

For HW/SW inventory views the limit was calculated for the number of entries
per row, not the number of rows, resulting in limit warnings even if the limit
was not exceeded.
